Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.02,1:11:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}Vậy à?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.13,1:11:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}Chà, kích thước giống nhau. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.70,1:11:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}
