Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.05,1:11:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.85,1:11:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs72}Tôi sẽ trở lại ngay.
